DATA CLOUD
Load Data from Data Cloud into Marketing Cloud Intelligence

Connect Data Cloud to Marketing Cloud Intelligence to analyze your customer data and build dashboards and reports.

The data is refreshed daily by default. You can change the frequency schedule, but using a different refresh rate could delay data subject rights and other compliance-based updates from flowing to Marketing Cloud Intelligence.

You can load your data using an Intelligence Data Cloud connector (TotalConnect or Granular Data Center) or by installing the Data Cloud app from the Intelligence Marketplace.

Another connector exists in Intelligence for Data Cloud (Data Cloud CI connector) and appears if you previously used it, or if you installed the Data Cloud app. However, we recommend using the Data Cloudconnectors instead. For more information, see Pull Data Cloud Data into Marketing Cloud Intelligence.

Before loading data from Data Cloud into Intelligence, review the prerequisites. See Prerequisites Before Pulling Data Cloud Data.
